msgstr "Bandbreite & Zeitfenster"

msgid "Bandwidth Limit"
msgstr "Bandbreiten-Limit"

msgid "Max download speed (KB/s)"
msgstr "Max. Download-Geschwindigkeit (KB/s)"

msgid ""
"Throttles all downloads to this speed. 0 = unlimited. Applies to new "
"downloads."
msgstr ""
"Drosselt alle Downloads auf diese Geschwindigkeit. 0 = unbegrenzt. Gilt "
"für neue Downloads."

msgid "Download Time Window"
msgstr "Download-Zeitfenster"

msgid "Only download during a specific time window"
msgstr "Nur innerhalb eines bestimmten Zeitfensters herunterladen"

msgid "From"
msgstr "Von"

msgid "Until"
msgstr "Bis"

msgid ""
"New downloads only start within this window (server local time). "
"Overnight windows like 22:00–06:00 are supported. Running downloads are "
"not interrupted."
msgstr ""
"Neue Downloads starten nur innerhalb dieses Fensters (lokale Serverzeit)."
" Über-Nacht-Fenster wie 22:00–06:00 werden unterstützt. Laufende "
"Downloads werden nicht unterbrochen."

