msgid "Adds your Crunchyroll watchlist series to the calendar — works even when the general Crunchyroll display is off, as long as a Crunchyroll account is configured. Episode dates come from TMDB (CineInfo API key required)."
msgstr "Fügt deine Crunchyroll-Watchlist-Serien zum Kalender hinzu — funktioniert auch, wenn die allgemeine Crunchyroll-Anzeige aus ist, solange ein Crunchyroll-Konto konfiguriert ist. Episodendaten kommen von TMDB (CineInfo-API-Key erforderlich)."

msgid "Adds the series from your Crunchyroll custom lists (Crunchylists) to the calendar — works even when the general Crunchyroll display is off, as long as a Crunchyroll account is configured. Episode dates come from TMDB (CineInfo API key required)."
